Package nl.tno.sensorstorm.api.particles

This package contains interfaces and abstract classes for defining Particles.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CustomParticlePojoMapper<T extends Particle>
    Custom mapper for a Particle.
    DataParticle
    A marker interface that indicates this particle is a DataParticle (instead of a MetaParticle).
    MetaParticle
    A marker interface that indicates this particle is a MetaParticle (instead of a DataParticle).
    Particle
    Defines a Particle.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDataParticle
    A default implementation of a Particle (for convenience).
    AbstractMetaParticle
    A default implementation of a MetaParticle (for convenience).
    AbstractParticle
    A default implementation of a Particle (for convenience).
    DataParticleBatch
    An extension of an ArrayList which forms a batch of DataParticles being created by a Batcher.
